articles.title: Twitter Reactions: Marco Jansen's all-round show steer South Africa to series-clinching win over Australia | SA vs AUS 2023, 5th ODI - Cricket Times
articles.description: South Africa sealed the five-match series against Australia with comprehensive win in the 5th ODI. Marco Jansen was named 'Player of the Match' for his all-round performance.
articles.content: In a fitting conclusion to the five-match ODI series, South Africa convincingly defeated Australia in the fifth and final game, sealing their victory with a resounding margin of 122 runs. The hosts’ … [+4754 chars]
